devdoc.details: Simple leaderboard contract for Banana Fever Dream game Stores best scores for each player address with basic validation

getAllPlayers().details: Get all player addresses (for off-chain sorting)

returns._0: Array of all player addresses who have submitted scores

getAllScores().details: Get all scores (for off-chain sorting and display)

returns._0: Total number of unique players who have submitted scores

returns.score: The player's best score (0 if never played)

submitScore(uint256).details: Submit a score to the leaderboard

params._score: The score to submit Requirements: - Score must be greater than 0 - Score must be better than player's current best score
